# Privacy Policy for JeruScore

**Effective Date:** September 30, 2024

JeruScore ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you visit or interact with our website.

## 1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:

### 1.1 Personal Information
When you register on our site, subscribe to a newsletter, or enter information, we may collect:
- Name
- Email address
- Phone number
- Payment information (if applicable)

### 1.2 Non-Personal Information
We may also collect non-personally identifiable information, including:
- Browser type
- Device type (e.g., mobile, desktop)
- IP address
- Browsing behavior on our site (e.g., pages visited, time spent)

## 2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for the following purposes:
- To personalize your experience on our website.
- To improve our website and services.
- To process your transactions and send updates regarding your order.
- To send periodic emails regarding promotions, news, or updates about our services.
- To comply with legal requirements or respond to lawful requests by public authorities.

## 3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We use cookies to enhance your experience. Cookies are small files that a site or its service provider transfers to your device’s hard drive through your web browser, allowing us to recognize your browser and remember certain information. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings.

## 4. Sharing of Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties, except when required to provide you with services, comply with the law, or protect our rights. This includes:
- Service providers who help us operate our website and business.
- Legal authorities when required by law.

## 5. Data Retention
We will retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

## 6. Security of Your Information
We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

## 7. Your Rights
You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
- **Access:** You have the right to access and receive a copy of the personal information we hold about you.
- **Rectification:** You can request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information.
- **Erasure:** You can request that we delete your personal information.
- **Data Portability:** You can request to receive your personal data in a structured, commonly used, and machine-readable format.

To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at [support@jeruscore.com](mailto:support@jeruscore.com).

## 8. Third-Party Links
Occasionally, at our discretion, we may include or offer third-party products or services on our website. These third-party sites have their own privacy policies, and we are not responsible for their content or practices.

## 9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the "Effective Date" at the top will be updated accordingly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

## 10. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the practices of our website, please contact us at:

**JeruScore Support Team**  
Email: [support@jeruscore.com](mailto:support@jeruscore.com)  
Phone: +1 (234) 567-890  
Address: 123 Football Avenue, Jerusalem

---

Thank you for trusting JeruScore with your data.

# Terms and Conditions for JeruScore

**Effective Date:** September 30, 2024

Welcome to JeruScore! These terms and conditions ("Terms") govern your use of our website and services. By accessing or using JeruScore, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of our site and services.

## 1. General Terms
By using JeruScore, you acknowledge and agree that:
- You are at least 18 years of age, or the legal age of majority in your jurisdiction.
- You will use our website and services in compliance with applicable laws and regulations.

## 2. Services Offered
JeruScore provides sports predictions, including:
- **Free Games:** Access to sports predictions and analysis for free.
- **VIP Games:** Premium predictions that come with a fee. These predictions are based on more detailed analysis and purchased data.

### Important Notice
While we offer deeply analyzed predictions, **neither Free Games nor VIP Games are fixed**. Our predictions are based on professional analysis, historical data, team performance, and other key indicators. **We do not guarantee the accuracy or outcome of any predictions** provided on our platform.

## 3. VIP Subscriptions and Payments
By subscribing to our VIP Games, you agree to the following:
- The VIP service requires payment, as we purchase critical data, software tools, and resources that contribute to the detailed analysis behind VIP predictions.
- Payments for VIP subscriptions are **non-refundable**, regardless of the outcome of the games.

### 3.1 Payment Methods
- Payments can be made through the payment methods available on our site.
- By making a purchase, you agree to pay all applicable fees and taxes associated with the service.

### 3.2 Non-Refundable Policy
Please note that **all payments are final and non-refundable**, even if you are dissatisfied with the performance of any predictions.

## 4. Use of Content
All content on JeruScore, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, and data, is the intellectual property of JeruScore. You may not reproduce, distribute, or otherwise use any content without prior written consent.

## 5. Limitation of Liability
JeruScore provides its services "as is" and makes no guarantees regarding the outcomes of sports events. We are not liable for any losses, including financial losses, incurred from following our predictions.

## 6. User Responsibilities
As a user of JeruScore, you agree that:
- You will not engage in any activity that disrupts or interferes with the operation of the website.
- You will not attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website or its services.

## 7. Links to Third-Party Websites
Our website may contain links to third-party websites. These sites are independent of JeruScore, and we are not responsible for their content or practices. Visiting these third-party websites is at your own risk, and you should review their terms and policies.

## 8. Modification of Terms
We reserve the right to modify or update these Terms at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated Terms.

## 9. Governing Law
These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of [Your Country/State]. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the website shall be resolved through the applicable legal processes in [Your Country/State].

## 10. Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding these Terms, feel free to contact us at:

**JeruScore Support Team**  
Email: [support@jeruscore.com](mailto:support@jeruscore.com)  
Phone: +1 (234) 567-890  
Address: 123 Football Avenue, Jerusalem

---

Thank you for choosing JeruScore!
